title: [Velathae, South Sunrise Road]
description: Weak streams of moonlight break through the thick, gloomy cloud-cover above, casting a dim light on the small splotches of withered grass that strangle the road.  Dead leaves are scattered about the area, damp with the chilly moisture that clings to the air.

Thin streams of dim light break through the thick, gloomy cloud-cover above.  Small splotches of brown grass strangle portions of the road, but have long since withered and passed.  Dead leaves are scattered about the area, damp with the chilly moisture that clings to the air.
